{"tid":764151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲Keep得似MK妹 姚嘉妮唔會出寫真：我無身材","createTime":"2018-08-01T17:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T05:48:35.000Z","uid":157545,"like":17,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec9eecafe82e083c0625aa6a50bb3e9199ebdd7","tid":764151,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/010338_741551f819e78dd30e01ac8dfe819995.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F010338_741551f819e78dd30e01ac8dfe819995.jpg&h=e73a0faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇集《BB來了》飾演陪月員朗朗的姚嘉妮，因為角色鮮明加上保養得宜而令風頭蓋過飾演其妹的高海寧。姚嘉妮感謝觀眾能夠接受到自己演「過氣MK妹」，稱自己的確有落足心機去演呢個角色。<br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮今次與吳家樂飾演嘅角色有愛情線，被網友大讚浪漫。姚嘉妮就透露：「我同家樂今次都好得意，嚟緊結局篇會有驚喜俾大家，大家可以拭目以待。」<br />\n<br />\n即將迎接40歲生日，姚嘉妮就透露會繼續做廿四孝媽咪：「依家啲生日都俾晒小朋友，只要切個蛋糕同佢哋一齊過就已經好開心。啱啱又同小朋友去完加拿大，所以都會留返喺香港過。」她亦笑言拍完《BB來了》幾乎所有觀眾都知道她的歲數：「踏入另一個字頭，我OK嘅，我接受呢個年齡。我唔覺得自己老，依然好有活力，而且要成日陪小朋友，更加要Keep得好。」問到最近被讚Keep得好，會否考慮出寫真留倩影，她笑言：「唔會，我無身材。我只係好鍾意做運動同跳舞，咁樣我都開心啲。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/010338_475cbdca8bf490c517c9135ba9e6ca60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F010338_475cbdca8bf490c517c9135ba9e6ca60.jpg&h=a72a03c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對腳正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75623b693281021099090f9ff80e427765b26ce3","tid":764151,"uid":3962,"like":26,"dislike":6,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"htt